latestIgtvVideos.title: IS YOU SKINCARE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Check out this revolutionary product from @is.you.skincare @shantalmujumdar ✨

Steps to use :- 

1. Cleanse your face using a face wash and pat dry.
2. Open the Bio-Molecules Activator jar. Press the white plate
down slowly to ooze out a small portion of cream.
3. As per the instructions chart, slowly add one pump of Skin
Molecules (1,2 or 3) on the Activator jar plate.
4. Mix the instructed combinations on the Activator jar plate.
Massage the obtained concoction gently along your jawline in
upward sweeping motions.
5.Sweep from your nose to your ears and across your forehead
and massage it over the cheeks to your temples. Apply from the
base of the neck to the tip of the chin and apply any excess
concotion over the décolleté.

Day 1 in Hong Kong 🇭🇰✨

Kickstart your adventure with a perfect blend of culture, views, and street vibes:

📍 Victoria Peak – Get a stunning panoramic view of the city skyline
📍 Man Mo Temple – A peaceful retreat with incense-filled history
📍 Hollywood Road & Central – Explore street art, antique shops, and chic cafes
📍 Tsim Sha Tsui Promenade – Walk along the harbour with views of the iconic skyline
📍 Avenue of Stars – Snap photos with Bruce Lee and soak in the film legacy

End the day with a Symphony of Lights show from the waterfront 🌃💫
